videos.description: Kyle Shurmur hits Trent Sherfield for a touchdown from 4 yards out to give Vanderbilt the lead on the opening drive.
videos.headline: Vandy scores TD on opening drive

videos.description: Mike White connects with Lucky Jackson for a 30-yard pass play to set up the Hilltoppers.
videos.headline: White to Jackson strikes big for Western Kentucky

videos.description: Nacarius Fant hits Quinton Baker on a trick play for a touchdown to tie the game at 7-7.
videos.headline: Western Kentucky's gadget play results in a TD

videos.description: Trent Sherfield's back shoulder catch producers a 30-yard gain for Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Sherfield rises and delivers a big play for Vandy

videos.description: Ralph Webb scores a touchdown from 8 yards out to reclaim the lead for Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Webb muscles in for Vandy TD

videos.description: Lucky Jackson's 54-yard catch sets up the Hilltoppers in scoring position.
videos.headline: White to Jackson strikes again for Western Kentucky

videos.description: Mike White's 3 yard touchdown run ties the game 14-14 late in the second quarter.
videos.headline: White stands tall for TD

videos.description: Kyle Shurmur's pass is deflected by Western Kentucky's Antwon Kincade and ricochets to Trey Ellis for a 31-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Crazy deflection leads to Vandy TD

videos.description: The punt deflects off of Vanderbilt's Frank Coppet's foot and Antwon Kincade is there for the recovery.
videos.headline: Western Kentucky recovers fumble on punt

videos.description: Trent Sherfield's 45-yard touchdown run on the reverse adds to the lead for Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Sherfield's TD extends the lead for Vandy

videos.description: Mike White's pass is complete to Nacarius Fant for a 28-yard gain that puts the Hilltoppers in the red zone.
videos.headline: Fant's catch and run puts Western Kentucky in the red zone

videos.description: Mike White's pass is incomplete intended for Lucky Jackson on fourth down to preserve the lead for Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Vandy's defense holds on 4th down

videos.description: Mike Couzens and John Congemi says Vanderbilt's playmakers were the difference in their 31-17 win against Western Kentucky.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt remains bowl eligiable
